WEBVTT

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:31.445
their brains predict
a hammering heartbeat,

00:12:31.469 --> 00:12:32.888
sweaty hands,

00:12:32.912 --> 00:12:38.412
so much so that they are unable
to actually take the test.

00:12:38.436 --> 00:12:39.698
They don't perform well,

00:12:39.722 --> 00:12:44.119
and sometimes they not only fail courses
but they actually might fail college.

00:12:45.131 --> 00:12:46.282
But here's the thing:

00:12:47.036 --> 00:12:50.848
a hammering heartbeat
is not necessarily anxiety.

00:12:50.872 --> 00:12:56.007
It could be that your body
is preparing to do battle

00:12:56.031 --> 00:12:57.515
and ace that test ...

00:12:58.449 --> 00:13:00.624
or, you know, give a talk